<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="2">Dear {!OnlineApplication__c.Contact_Name__c},<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="2">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Thank you for your interest in the FleetPro Services OTR Card program.&nbsp;For your convenience, I’ve attached a link to our online application.&nbsp;Please note that the name listed on the Business Service Agreement (BSA) must be EXACTLY the same as the name used to sign the application.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif"><font size="2">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Please <a href="{!OnlineApplication__c.External_Application_URL__c}">click on this link</a>&nbsp;and follow the instructions to complete your application process.&nbsp; Thank you.</font></p></div><div><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="2">Again, thank you for&nbsp;your interest in the FleetPro Services OTR Card. If you have any questions about the application, please don’t hesitate to call or email me.<br><br>Sincerely,<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><o:p><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><o:p><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><a name="Text10">{!User.Name}</a><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="2">{!User.Title}<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="2"></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="2">{!User.CompanyName}</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font size="2"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif">Phone: {!User.Phone}</font><a name="Text12"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif">&nbsp; &nbsp;</font></a></font></p>]]></td>
